</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="1" ind2=" " tag="561">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Possible ownership inscription:  Brother Pietro di Santo Giovanni (Frater Petrus de Sancto Joanne), Florence (?), 1399 (inscription, f. 9v).</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="1" ind2=" " tag="561">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Sold at auction at Sotheby's, 2 Dec. 1986, lot 35, to Lawrence J. Schoenberg.</marc:subfield>
